        ('"\\"Thou dost need me, father. Thy business is much too complex for thee to run by thyself!\\""', '"「你需要我，父親。你的生意太複雜了，你一個人經營不來！」"'),
        ('"\\"Ah, er... I can do fine without thee, my dear.\\""', '"「啊，呃……沒有妳我也能做得很好，親愛的。」"'),
        ('"\\"Hmmm... what were we discussing, "', '"「嗯……我們剛才在討論什麼， "'),
