        ('"\\"I went to open my shop the next morning and there was a bundle of food in place of the Filari Alyssand had put there the night before.\\""', '"「第二天早上我去開店時，發現 Alyssand 前一天晚上放在那裡的菲拉利幣( Filari )不見了，取而代之的是一包食物。」"'),
        ('"@That is what happened to our food!@"', '"@這就是我們食物的下落！@"'),
