        ('"\\"Thou must be a stranger...\\""', '"「你一定是個陌生人……」"'),
        ('"\\"Filari are Fawn\'s currency... A small silver disk with a colored gem in the center.\\""', '"「菲拉利幣( Filari )是幼鹿城( Fawn )的貨幣……一種中間鑲有彩色寶石的銀色小圓盤。」"'),
        ('"\\"Yes... yes. Those are Filari.\\""', '"「是的……是的。那些就是菲拉利幣( Filari )。」"'),
